{"id":2355,"date":"2021-04-01T13:10:31","date_gmt":"2021-04-01T13:10:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/?p=2355"},"modified":"2021-07-30T16:16:55","modified_gmt":"2021-07-30T16:16:55","slug":"bao-nhieu-calo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/bao-nhieu-calo\/","title":{"rendered":"1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o bao nhi\u00eau calo? \u0102n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o t\u0103ng c\u00e2n hay gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/a> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng r\u1ea5t cao. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u0103n kho\u0103n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft 1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o bao nhi\u00eau calo, \u0103n nhi\u1ec1u Y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e9o hay kh\u00f4ng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc n\u00e0y!<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong>1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o bao nhi\u00eau calo?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n \u0103n c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng r\u1ea5t cao. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng 1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o bao nhi\u00eau calo th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2357\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2357\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2357 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/mot-chen-yen-bao-nhieu-calo.jpg\" alt=\"1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn bao nhi\u00eau calo l\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/mot-chen-yen-bao-nhieu-calo.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/mot-chen-yen-bao-nhieu-calo-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/mot-chen-yen-bao-nhieu-calo-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2357\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn bao nhi\u00eau calo l\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><strong>\u0110\u1ecbnh l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo trong 1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo b\u1ea3ng t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo, 100 gram Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 345KCal. N\u00f3 cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi 100 gram c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ecbt b\u00f2 &#8211;\u00a0 250 Kcal, th\u1ecbt heo &#8211; 242 Kcal, c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i &#8211; 208 Kcal. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5, Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn.\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng 5 gram \u0111\u1ebfn 10 gram t\u1ed5 Y\u1ebfn. Quy \u0111\u1ed5i ra th\u00ec 1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u1ebd kho\u1ea3ng 18 \u0111\u1ebfn 35 Kcal.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1712\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1712\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-1712 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/che-to-yen-hat-sen-copy.jpg\" alt=\"Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo kh\u00e1 cao n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00edt m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0103n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/che-to-yen-hat-sen-copy.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/che-to-yen-hat-sen-copy-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/che-to-yen-hat-sen-copy-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1712\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo kh\u00e1 cao n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00edt m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0103n<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00f2n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u00f3 trong c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb Y\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u201cN\u01b0\u1edbc Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a bao nhi\u00eau calo?\u201d, \u201cN\u01b0\u1edbc Y\u1ebfn nha \u0111am bao nhi\u00eau calo?\u201d.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/thanh-phan-dinh-duong-to-yen\/\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 trong 100g y\u1ebfn<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u1ee9a kho\u1ea3ng 242 kcal.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100 ml n\u01b0\u1edbc Y\u1ebfn nha \u0111am ch\u1ee9a 64 kcal.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">100 ml Y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e8n ch\u1ee9a 321 kcal.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>\u0102n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f3 g\u00e2y t\u0103ng c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1825\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1825\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-1825 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/yen-sao-giam-can.jpg\" alt=\"Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n ki\u00eang c\u00f2n lo ng\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 g\u00e2y t\u0103ng c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/yen-sao-giam-can.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/yen-sao-giam-can-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/yen-sao-giam-can-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1825\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n ki\u00eang c\u00f2n lo ng\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 g\u00e2y t\u0103ng c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf n\u1eef gi\u1edbi m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y n\u00ean n\u1ea1p kho\u1ea3ng 1000 &#8211; 1500 Kcal, \u1edf nam gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 2000 &#8211; 2300 Kcal (\u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0103n ki\u00eang gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n). Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo \u1edf Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o kh\u00e1 cao. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 600 gram Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c trong ng\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ea1p v\u00e0o c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft s\u1ebd g\u00e2y d\u01b0 th\u1eeba v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u0103ng c\u00e2n.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0102n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 b\u00e9o hay kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0103n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 \u0103n v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf kho\u1ea3ng 1 ch\u00e9n 5 gram th\u00ec m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ea1p v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng cao, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u0103ng c\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0103n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn th\u1eeba s\u1ed1 calo c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, g\u00e2y n\u00ean t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u0103ng c\u00e2n.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng trong Y\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t. V\u00ec v\u1eady, lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0103n ki\u00eang, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><strong>U\u1ed1ng Y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c u\u1ed1ng, \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 b\u0103n kho\u0103n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft \u0103n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, Y\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n.\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n ki\u00eang th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n.\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\nXem th\u00eam:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/yen-sao-cho-nguoi-giam-can\/\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n c\u00f3 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng? V\u00ec sao?<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><strong>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i protein, axit amin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t vi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a 31 nguy\u00ean t\u1ed1 vi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a 50 &#8211; 60% protein gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 axit aspartic gi\u00fap s\u1ea3n sinh globulin, t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n Threonine gi\u00fap th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a gan.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee9a Fructose, Isoleucine gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, b\u1ed5 sung n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho b\u1ec7nh nh\u00e2n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t, Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. Gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u1ed1m d\u1eady, t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng, t\u1ed1t cho tim m\u1ea1ch, huy\u1ebft \u00e1p v\u00e0 th\u1ea7n kinh, gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb \u0103n ngon mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u0103ng &#8211; gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n (t\u00f9y theo t\u1eebng c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng).<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong>C\u00e1ch \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng &#8211; gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n. V\u1eady <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/huong-dan-su-dung-yen-sao\/\">\u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n?<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1735\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1735\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-1735 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/tac-dung-yen-voi-nguoi-gay.jpg\" alt=\"T\u00f9y v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch \u0103n v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n m\u00e0 Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/tac-dung-yen-voi-nguoi-gay.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/tac-dung-yen-voi-nguoi-gay-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/tac-dung-yen-voi-nguoi-gay-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1735\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00f9y v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch \u0103n v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n m\u00e0 Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><strong>C\u00e1ch \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong t\u1ed5 Y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i axit amin c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ngon mi\u1ec7ng, t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tinh th\u1ea7n, gi\u00fap t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng lu\u00f4n vui v\u1ebb, t\u0103ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t, protein c\u00f3 trong Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u0169ng gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. L\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 Y\u1ebfn c\u0169ng cao n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u00e2n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7y r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u00e2n th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n trong nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0103n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n 3 l\u1ea7n, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00e9n nh\u1ecf. N\u00ean \u0103n c\u00e1ch ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a.\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u1eeb Y\u1ebfn gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u00e2n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7y l\u00e0: Y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e8n, Y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng l\u00e1 d\u1ee9a, Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1t sen. C\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd n\u00ean \u0103n Y\u1ebfn sau khi d\u00f9ng b\u1eefa ch\u00ednh kho\u1ea3ng 1 &#8211; 2 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0103n m\u1ed7i b\u1eefa.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><strong>C\u00e1ch \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. B\u1edfi Y\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00e8m \u0103n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n ki\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n \u0103n ki\u00eang b\u1eb1ng Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tinh b\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1m trong b\u1eefa ch\u00ednh. \u0102n nhi\u1ec1u rau v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y. Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho b\u1eefa chi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c mu\u1ed1n \u0103n v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i. Ho\u1eb7c, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n Y\u1ebfn l\u00e0m b\u1eefa \u0103n t\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0103n ki\u00eang. B\u1edfi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u00e2y t\u0103ng c\u00e2n nhanh nh\u1ea5t cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o t\u1ef1 ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0ng. Kh\u00f4ng u\u1ed1ng Y\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3ng lon s\u1eb5n v\u00ec c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t cao.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ec9 \u0103n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 n\u00ean \u0103n c\u00e1ch ng\u00e0y. M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0103n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 gram.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee1 th\u1eeba trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u 1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o bao nhi\u00eau Calo. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n cho t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Hi v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng r\u1ea5t cao. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u0103n kho\u0103n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft 1 ch\u00e9n Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o bao nhi\u00eau calo, \u0103n nhi\u1ec1u Y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e9o hay kh\u00f4ng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng th\u1eafc [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2357,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"none"},"categories":[19],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2355"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2355"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2355\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2357"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2355"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2355"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2355"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}